productInfo.planAbout: In life's journey, health is always the most important asset, accompanying you through each stage. Realizing this, Team 01 proudly introduces Health Insurance Plan 01, a perfect choice to protect you and your loved ones. Our health insurance plan not only provides peace of mind in treating serious illnesses but also helps reduce financial burdens, ensuring you can focus on recovery and enjoy life. The XX Insurance Package includes basic insurance benefits up to an impressive value, allowing you to choose reputable medical facilities nationwide. Especially, no health check is required before participation, making the registration process quick and convenient. In addition, we offer a variety of insurance benefits, from inpatient to outpatient treatment, personal accident insurance, life, dental, and maternity, ensuring comprehensive protection for you and your family. Our insurance package is very diverse, from Vietnamese citizens to foreigners residing in Vietnam, from 15-day-old children to 60-year-old adults, with the ability to renew up to 65 years old. This flexibility ensures that everyone can be protected under the care of 01. Let Team 01 accompany you, protect the most valuable asset of life - health, helping you and your family always feel secure and happy
